{"type": "article", "id": 23605, "title": "Kate & Kate 冬季纺织品系列", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-10T07:30:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606155819MWDbVGqv4jKN3wgp.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是澳大利亚做纺织设计的品牌 Kate &amp; Kate 推出的 2016 冬季系列，包括毯子、垫子、枕套等棉纺织品。他们擅长用不同颜色的色块做出拼接效果，比如方形的色块大小深浅错落排列，很有艺术感。也有方格、条纹等普通的样式，但色调偏灰，偶尔使用粉色或蓝色提亮，给人柔和舒适的感受。售价 119 美元起，<a href=\"http://kateandkate.com.au/shop/category/new/\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155817rknJDpENK7folc3M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.41333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155817iBN30kjtH5wzy6P1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.18166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155817wsGrybmXuJFxRL53.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.31333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155818TLpPQsUEkuOzfarJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.39666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155819urL5YUX2TneSI4ck.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.39166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}